      <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5"><tr><td><font face="  Times, Times New Roman, serif" class="bfont"><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td colspan="2"><font face="Tolk, Times, serif" class="h1font">Rangers and Orc Dangers</font></td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Papy, Times, serif" class="h2font"> Rating</Font></TD><TD><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><font size=1>(4.67)</font> | <A HREF="/lotr/decks/decks.php?reviews=21480">Read Reviews</A></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Papy, Times, serif" class="h2font"> Author</font></TD><TD><font face="  Times, Times New Roman, serif" class="bfont"> <A HREF="http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=9416">Alan "admiraldenny" Denny</A></FONT> <font face="Papy, Times, serif" class="afont"> <a href='http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=9416&sub=1'> (Subscribe to this member)</a></font></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Papy, Times, serif" class="h2font"> Description</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="  Times, Times New Roman, serif" class="bfont"> This deck relies on the Rangers to move the fellowship safely and direct and indirect damage from Sauren Orcs.</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Papy, Times, serif" class="h2font"> Submitted</Font></TD><TD><font face="  Times, Times New Roman, serif" class="bfont"> February 16, 2002</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Papy, Times, serif" class="h2font"> Cards</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="  Times, Times New Roman, serif" class="bfont"> Starting:<br>
